        " «يُغَسِّلُهَا أَوْلَى اَلنَّاسِ بِهَا مِنَ اَلرِّجَالِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.432 - Ammar al-Sabati asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a young girl for whom no woman is available to wash her.\nImam (as) replied: \"The one most closely related to her among the men should wash her.\""
        ]
